âœ… 3. (Optional but Recommended): Install "Live Server" Extension
This extension helps you preview your HTML in a browser live (auto-refreshes on save):
In VS Code, go to Extensions (left bar or press Ctrl+Shift+X)
Search for Live Server by Ritwick Dey
Click Install
Now right-click your index.html file and select "Open with Live Server"

